tially critical, and draws on the findings of recent Japanese scholarship.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aLiterary Studies -- Asian. 4aLiterature -- Theater, Poetry, and Fiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Poetry.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503620735423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503620735/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles